findingsText:
 Grant started in Spring 2014, too early to tell. Too early to tell but guided by insights from grant case studies we plan to:
(1) develop a suite of software tools to support various aspects of data analysis and curation;
(2) provide guidance on ethical considerations surrounding analysis of social media data;
deliver training workshops for social science researchers
(3) engage with the public on this important topic through a series of festivals (food, music, science). Aerospace, Defence and Marine,Communities and Social Services/Policy,Creative Economy,Digital/Communication/Information Technologies (including Software),Education,Government, Democracy and Justice,Culture, Heritage, Museums and Collections,Retail,Security and Diplomacy,Transport
